import React from 'react' import { useForm } from 'react-hook-form' import { useDispatch } from 'react-redux' import { registerUser } from '../redux/actions/authActions' export default function Register() { const { register, handleSubmit, reset } = useForm() const dispatch = useDispatch() const onSubmit = (data) => { let updatedData = { ...data, houseNumber: parseInt(data.houseNumber), zip: parseInt(data.zip), isAdmin: 0, } console.log('this is the data', updatedData) dispatch(registerUser(updatedData)) setTimeout(() => reset(), 5000) } return (
) }
